.Dd April 12, 2026
.Dt PKG 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm pkg
.Nd personal package manager for macOS user prefixes
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar command
.Op Ar args
.Nm
.Cm help
.Op Ar command
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
manages packages in the user prefix under
.Pa ~/.local .
CLI and runtime packages are installed under
.Pa ~/.local/opt
and exposed through
.Pa ~/.local/bin .
Managed GUI applications are installed in
.Pa ~/Applications .
.Pp
The command set is intentionally small and follows a ports-style workflow:
.Bl -tag -width indent
.It Cm list
List registry packages.
.It Cm search
Search registry packages.
.It Cm installed
List installed packages.
.It Cm show
Show registry metadata for a package.
.It Cm info
Show installed package state from the manifest.
.It Cm install
Install a package.
.It Cm reinstall
Remove and install the current package version.
.It Cm remove
Remove a package.
.It Cm upgrade
Upgrade one package or all installed packages with
.Cm --all .
.It Cm self-upgrade
Refresh
.Nm
itself from the configured bootstrap source.
.It Cm cleanup
Remove build state, and optionally cached downloads.
.It Cm audit
Report integrity-policy problems in the registry.
.It Cm version
Show installed
.Nm
bootstrap metadata.
.It Cm doctor
Print installation paths and environment diagnostics.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "~/.local/share/pkg/completions/zsh/_pkg"
.It Pa ~/.local/bin
User-visible command symlinks and wrappers.
.It Pa ~/.local/opt
Versioned package payloads.
.It Pa ~/.local/share/pkg
Package state, manifests, caches, completions, and runtime files.
.It Pa ~/.config/pkg
Bootstrap and release configuration.
.It Pa ~/.local/share/pkg/completions/zsh/_pkg
Installed zsh completion for
.Nm .
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Bd -literal -offset indent
pkg install bun
pkg show python
pkg info google-chrome
pkg upgrade --all
pkg self-upgrade
pkg cleanup --cache
.Ed
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
.Bl -tag -width "PKG_BOOTSTRAP_REPO"
.It Ev PKG_RELEASE_REPO
Default GitHub release repository used by
.Cm :github-release
packages.
.It Ev PKG_BOOTSTRAP_REPO
Bootstrap repository used by
.Cm self-upgrade .
.It Ev PKG_BOOTSTRAP_REF
Bootstrap ref used by
.Cm self-upgrade .
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr janet 1
.Sh AUTHORS
.Nm
is maintained by Mayphus.
